# No Border Radius

Do not use border-radius anywhere in the project. This includes:

- No `rounded`, `rounded-*` Tailwind classes
- No `border-radius` in CSS
- No `borderRadius` in inline styles or theme config

The app should have sharp, square corners everywhere. No exceptions.
